snippet.title: Mind Control DLC for Rocketbirds 2 on STEAM
snippet.description: We have implemented our most requested feature - total mind control pwnage! "I gotta take a huge dump!" - yes yes... all that stuff, but now in sandbox-y form for the game's Rescue Missions. Since it's about mind control, you'll also get politicians costumes, our politicians, like Big G and Putzki Jr (mini-Putzki) as new playable characters and that very special baseball cap and badge. Let's make Albatropolis Great again!
